title: Grateful Dead Live at Delta Center on 1995-02-19
lineage: Fostex D5 DAT (playback of DAT Master record) @ 16-bits, 48 kHz (S/PDIF optical out) > M-Audio Firewire Audiophile external soundcard > Magix Sound Forge Pro Suite 12.1 build 170 x64  Audacity used for tracking, tagging, flac8 conversion
description:
Set I
Jack Straw
Sugaree
Walkin' Blues
Alabama Getaway *
Me & My Uncle >
Big River
Don't Ease Me In
Set II
China Cat Sunflower >
I Know You Rider
Samson & Delilah
If The Shoe Fits
New Speedway Boogie
Estimated Prophet >
Drums >
Space >
I Need A Miracle >
Attics Of My Life >
Johnny B. Goode

Encore:
It's All Over Now Baby Blue
Set III
Soundcheck:

Alabama Getaway
Attics Of My Life
Good Morning Little Schoolgirl
It's A Man's World
Comment
First Performance since June 18, 1989 *

Jerry Garcia - Guitar
Bob Weir - Guitar
Vince Welnick - Keyboards
Phil Lesh - Bass
Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Mickey Hart - Drums
